scene.message:
Clerk: Oh, Mayuzumi, you're{nl}
early. Your shift hasn't{nl}
started yet, has it? Need{nl}
something?{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: Something came up{nl}
suddenly... I'll be a little{nl}
late for my shift. I'll make{nl}
up for it by staying longer.{waitkey}{ret}

Clerk: Ah, that's fine. My,{nl}
you're dedicated. Having a{nl}
goal really does make a{nl}
difference, doesn't it.{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: I can't even imagine{nl}
Mayuzumi in that uniform,{nl}
smiling away.{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: Open for business even{nl}
with demons about — quite{nl}
admirable.{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: Yukino, working a job{nl}
seriously... So what's this{nl}
goal of hers?{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: I wonder if the demons{nl}
won't come inside the store.{nl}
Either way, it's a relief.{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: I want to study{nl}
abroad and learn photography{nl}
over there. That's why I'm{nl}
saving up money.{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: Maybe I said{nl}
something irresponsible.{nl}
There's no guarantee of{nl}
anything, after all.{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: It's a strange feeling.{nl}
Being here, I start to wonder{nl}
if all of it was just{nl}
a dream.{waitkey}{ret}

Clerk: M-Mayuzumi! A-a{nl}
monster appeared! Please,{nl}
stay here with me!{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: I'm sorry, but I{nl}
have to go. If you stay{nl}
inside, you'll surely be{nl}
all right.{waitkey}{ret}

Clerk: ...{wait_fr:16}I'll be okay if I{nl}
stay inside, right?{wait_fr:21} I have to{nl}
keep the store open... we're{nl}
open year-round, after all...{waitkey}Welcome!{waitkey}{ret}
